  <entry>
    <title>IDA动态调试ELF文件</title>
    <url>/2021/04/12/IDA%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95ELF%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>IDA动态调试ELF文件</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="IDA动态调试ELF文件"><a href="#IDA动态调试ELF文件" class="headerlink" title="IDA动态调试ELF文件"></a>IDA动态调试ELF文件</h2><ul>
<li>找到<code>IDA根目录</code>，复制<code>linux_server</code>到<code>linux</code>系统中</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">32</span>位: IDA目录\dbgsrv\linux_server</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">64</span>位: IDA目录\dbgsrv\linux_server64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>在<code>linux</code>中，进入<code>linux_server</code>所在目录，给<code>linux_server</code>赋予可执行权限</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ chmod +x linux_server64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>启动linux_server</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./linux_server64</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>在<code>windows</code>端打开对应版本<code>IDA</code>，菜单栏中<code>Debugger--&gt;Run--&gt;Romote Linux debugger</code></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/jXTlWQ9k1G5wnyJ.png" alt="image-20210412235436807"></p>
<blockquote>
<pre>
Application: 要调试程序路径
Directory: 存放呗调试程序的路径
Hostname：linux主机的ip地址
其它默认
</pre>
</blockquote>
<p>ok即可进入<code>IDA</code>动态调试。</p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>IDA</tag>
        <tag>病毒分析</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>NexT主题优化</title>
    <url>/2021/04/14/NexT%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>NexT主题优化</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h4 id="添加站内搜索功能"><a href="#添加站内搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="添加站内搜索功能"></a>添加站内搜索功能</h4><p>参考链接：<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html#local-search">http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html#local-search</a></p>
<ol>
<li>下载插件</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm install hexo<span class="literal">-generator</span><span class="literal">-searchdb</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>配置站点配置文件<code>E:\code\blog\_config.yml</code>，新增以下内容到任意位置：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">10000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>编辑主题配置文件<code>E:\code\blog\themes\next\_config.yml</code>，搜索：<code>local_search</code>，将 enable的 <code>false</code>改为<code>true</code></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Local Search</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Dependencies: https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果：</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414002616875.png" alt="image-20210414002616875"></p>
<h4 id="添加评论系统"><a href="#添加评论系统" class="headerlink" title="添加评论系统"></a>添加评论系统</h4><ol>
<li>注册<a href="https://www.leancloud.cn/">LeanClound</a>，获取APP ID 和 APP Key，注册成功后，创建应用</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414010509279.png" alt="image-20210414010509279"></p>
<p><strong>参考文档</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://valine.js.org/">Valine</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>博客搭建</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>NexT</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>PicGo+Typora+Gitee配置图床</title>
    <url>/2021/04/12/PicGo+Typora+Gitee%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>PicGo+Typora+Gitee配置图床</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<blockquote>
<h2 id="0x1-PicGo"><a href="#0x1-PicGo" class="headerlink" title="0x1 PicGo"></a>0x1 PicGo</h2></blockquote>
<ul>
<li>下载插件</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/Zpsze56VDAqYJkN.png" alt="image-20210412074002547"></p>
<ul>
<li>设置图床</li>
</ul>
<p>打开PicGo–&gt;图床设置–&gt;Gitee图床–&gt;设置相关选项</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/dflEweIJWAj2K1B.png" alt="image-20210412074326384"></p>
<ul>
<li>配置gitee私人令牌</li>
</ul>
<p>设置–&gt;安全设置–&gt;私人令牌–&gt;生成私人令牌，记住私人令牌，复制到上图中的 token 选项中。</p>
<blockquote>
<h2 id="0x2-Typora"><a href="#0x2-Typora" class="headerlink" title="0x2 Typora"></a>0x2 Typora</h2></blockquote>
<p>打开typora–&gt;偏好设置–&gt;图像</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/mC41r2bo7RqvZyN.png" alt="image-20210412074833360"></p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>总结：</p>
<ul>
<li>下载PicGo–&gt;下载Gitee图床插件–&gt;配置该插件</li>
<li>申请gitee私人令牌</li>
<li>配置typora图像设置为上传服务</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>PicGo</tag>
        <tag>typora</tag>
        <tag>图床</tag>
      </tags>
